  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Laid es zaar tawu Sein- \ntus/ Wihrus un Seewas/ un\nmi eemu/ es pa Zeltu ween eefchu/\nBehrnixus/ mehs ne atlizzina-\nes ne atkahpschu ne pa labbo nedēs\njam ne weenu.\npa kreifo Rohku."
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pahrdohd man Barribu\npar Naudu/ ka es ehst warru/\nun dohd man Uhdeut par Nau-\ndu/ ka es dsert warru/ es tikkai\nKahjahm zaureefschu."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ittin ka man darrijschi\nirr Eesawa Behrni/ kas Sēirā\ndsihwo/ un tee Moabiteri/ kas\neeksch Arra dsihwo/ teekams es\nnahku pahr to Jardann us to\nSemmi/ ko tas KUNGS muh-\nfu Deews mums dohs."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Sions tas Rehniasch\nno Esbona ne gribbeja mums\nlikt pahreet/ jo tas KUNGS\ntaws Deews likke winna Prah-\ntam apzeetinatees/ un winna\nSirdi drohschai mestees/ tapehz\nka wiꞥsch to tawā Rohkā no-\nDohu/ ittin ka tas schodeen irr."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS fazzija\nus man: Reds/ Es efimu eesah-\nzis nodoht tewis Breekschā Sto-\nnu un winna Semmi/ fahz ee-\nmantoht winna Semmi."
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Sions iṣgahje mums\npretti/ wiꞥsch ar wiffem fa-\nweem Laudim Karā uhs Jahzu."
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tas KUNGS muh-\nfu Deews nodohe winnu muh-\nfu Preekschā/ un mehs kawain\nwinnu/ un winna Dehlus/ un\nwiffus winna Laudis."
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un mehs usjehnant tanni\nRaikā wiffus winna Pilssahthus/\nisdeldejam wiffus Pilshah-"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tohs Lohpus tikkai effam\nmehs preeksch mums xehmuschi/\nun to Pilssfahtu Laupijumu/ ko\nmehs usjehnam."
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No Aroera lihds Arno-\nna Uppes Kraſtam/ un ta Pilss-\nfahta/ kas pee Uppes irr lihds Gi-\nleadai/ ne weens Pilssfahts bija/\nkas preeksch mums warreja twer-\nters/ wiffus nodeewe tas Klungs\nmuhfu Deews muhfu Preekschā."
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bes ween us Ammonia\nBehrnu Semmi tu ne effi nah-\nzis/ nedē pee wiffa/ kas garr Ja-\nboka Uppes bija/ nedē pee teen\nPilssfahteem/ kas us Kalneem/\nnedē pee wiffa/ ko tas Klungs\nmuhfu Deews bij aisleedsis."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ehz to mehs atgreeſu\nBschees gabjam us aug-\nschu pa Bahsana Zeltu\nun Ogs tas Rehniasch no Bah-\nsana gabje mums pretti/ wiꞥsc\nar wiffem jaweem Laudim Ka-\nrā prett Eedreju."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas KUNGS\nuhs man: Ne bihstees preeks-\nwinnu/ jo es efimu winnu/ u-\nwiffus winna Laudis/ un win-\nSemini tawā Rohkā dewis/ u-\ntew buhs winnam darriht/ itt"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
